<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>The Friends Turning Bundt Cake into Big Business</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="The Friends Turning Bundt Cake into Big Business" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160504212434-nothing-bundt-cakes.jpeg" rel="share" />

